MINI-GAME ASSETS

Place the following PNG files in this directory:

- minigame-dash-icon.png (icon for Math Dash mini-game)
- minigame-match-icon.png (icon for Shape Match mini-game)
- falling-number.png (sprite for falling numbers in dash game)
- shape-icons.png (sprite sheet with circle, square, triangle icons)

These assets support the Mini-Games & Variety Breaks feature.
Recommended:

- Icons: 128x128px
- Sprites: 64x64px (or larger if sprite sheet)
